## Baseline Engineering Assumptions (v0.1)

This concept is modeled around the following reference case:

- IT Load: 10 MW (mid-scale AI deployment)
- Cooling Mode: Dry-first vertical radiator tower with VFD fan assist
- Rack Loop: 40°C supply / 50°C return (warm-water compatible)
- Design Ambient: 35°C dry bulb
- Target Approach: 7–10°C above ambient at peak
- Coil Pressure Drop Target: ≤10 Pa (draft-assist viable)
- Not intended as full chiller replacement
- Intended as fan/runtime reduction + recirculation control layer
- Geothermal = assist loop, not sole rejection mechanism

All values subject to refinement based on partner engineering input.


